1.10	ADIDAS	Adidas	Adidas AG is a sports apparel manufacturer and parent company of the Adidas Group, which consists of the Reebok sportswear company, TaylorMade-Adidas golf company (including Ashworth), and Rockport. Besides sports footwear, the company also produces other products such as bags, shirts, watches, eyewear, and other sports- and clothing-related goods. The company is the largest sportswear manufacturer in Europe and the second biggest sportswear manufacturer in the world.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Adidas_Logo.svg/200px-Adidas_Logo.svg.png
